metadata.name: Open Edition
metadata.description: A limited edition (69), titled "Open Edition." This was created to commemorate the Q1 2023 meta. I will then introduce a...oh boy, sorry to say, burn mechanic (you will need 2,) once this meta cycle ends in pain for some. That piece will be called, "Closed Edition." I'm not an artist. If this OE meta ends in pain for you, fear not, you bought it for the art did you not anon? ;)
